00:21:00,011 --> 00:21:00,760
Masakit yun.

251
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:09,752
Ano na, Fah?

252
00:21:11,457 --> 00:21:14,093
Na-discharge na ako, pero nasasaktan pa rin ako.

253
00:21:14,752 --> 00:21:15,899
Maaari ko bang i-extend ang aking bakasyon?

254
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:19,327
Hindi nakikita sa labas ang sugat ko, Fah.

255
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:22,490
But honestly, I'm in really bad shape, you get me?

256
00:21:23,484 --> 00:21:24,093
Oo.

257
00:21:25,022 --> 00:21:27,802
Kung hindi niya gusto, hindi ko alam kung bakit niya pinagdaanan iyon.

258
00:21:28,751 --> 00:21:30,650
I've told him so many times, hindi lang siya nakikinig.

259
00:21:31,238 --> 00:21:32,911
Bago pa man ang medical exam.

260
00:21:34,065 --> 00:21:36,082
Sabi ko "Kung hindi mo gusto ang isang bagay, huwag mong pilitin."

261
00:21:36,145 --> 00:21:37,699
"Sinasaktan mo lang ang sarili mo."

262
00:21:40,117 --> 00:21:41,862
Pero gusto daw niyang mag-aral ng medicine.

263
00:21:42,117 --> 00:21:43,453
Dahil sa mama niya diba?

264
00:21:44,478 --> 00:21:45,090
Oo.

265
00:21:46,648 --> 00:21:49,115
Nangako siya kay Emma noong may sakit ito

266
00:21:49,253 --> 00:21:51,191
na siya ay naging isang doktor upang gamutin siya.

267
00:21:51,586 --> 00:21:54,000
Ngunit hindi ko makita kung bakit kailangan iyon.

268
00:21:54,423 --> 00:21:58,804
Si Emma mismo ay malamang na ayaw niyang tiisin ang isang bagay na kinasusuklaman niya.

269
00:22:00,863 --> 00:22:01,967
totoo yan.

270
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,754
Kung ikaw ang nagsasabi nito,

271
00:22:07,832 --> 00:22:09,110
baka makinig siya.

272
00:22:14,762 --> 00:22:16,560
Oo, tulungan mo akong magbakasyon.

273
00:22:17,360 --> 00:22:18,490
Susubukan ko.

274
00:22:29,088 --> 00:22:31,080
Mahuhuli na kami ng professor.

275
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,485
Hindi na kailangang sunduin ako.

276
00:22:32,742 --> 00:22:33,976
Babalik ako sa North.

277
00:22:37,552 --> 00:22:39,745
Sabihin mo sa North na laslasan ko ang kanyang mga gulong.

278
00:22:41,285 --> 00:22:44,108
seryoso ako. Huwag mo akong sunduin.

279
00:22:44,533 --> 00:22:45,641
O magagalit ako.

280
00:22:47,681 --> 00:22:48,441
Sige.

281
00:22:52,253 --> 00:22:53,290
Magandang trabaho.

282
00:22:58,395 --> 00:22:59,324
Magkano ang sigarilyo?

283
00:23:00,777 --> 00:23:01,954
Magkano ang sigarilyo?

284
00:23:06,857 --> 00:23:07,592
Isang daan bawat isa.

285
00:23:07,850 --> 00:23:09,885
Ilagay mo sa tab ko. Nasa kwarto ko ang pera.

286
00:24:55,952 --> 00:24:56,952
Ikaw ba mismo ang sumulat nito?

287
00:24:57,564 --> 00:24:58,131
Oo.

288
00:25:00,348 --> 00:25:01,232
Sa totoo lang,

289
00:25:01,382 --> 00:25:02,491
Sinimulan ko ito kanina.

290
00:25:02,785 --> 00:25:03,782
Pero katatapos ko lang.

291
00:25:04,826 --> 00:25:06,208
Ang ganda talaga ng kanta.

292
00:25:07,807 --> 00:25:08,592
Napakatalented mo.

293
00:25:09,419 --> 00:25:10,447
Sa tingin mo?

294
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,062
Hindi mo lang ako niloloko, tama?

295
00:25:12,632 --> 00:25:15,567
Bakit ako? Ito ay talagang mabuti.

296
00:25:16,148 --> 00:25:16,567
Mm.

297
00:25:18,210 --> 00:25:19,358
Maaari ko bang makita ito?

298
00:25:21,155 --> 00:25:21,619
Oo naman.

299
00:25:25,525 --> 00:25:27,964
Sa totoo lang,

300
00:25:28,950 --> 00:25:31,733
Akala ko ay sinusulat ko lang ito para sa kasiyahan tulad ng mga nakaraang panahon.

301
00:25:32,478 --> 00:25:34,120
Pero nung naisip ko yung mukha mo,

302
00:25:34,840 --> 00:25:36,457
Bigla kong gustong seryosohin.

303
00:25:38,571 --> 00:25:40,770
Kaya ang kantang ito ay...

304
00:25:41,614 --> 00:25:42,613
Isinulat para sa iyo.

305
00:25:48,105 --> 00:25:49,188
salamat po.

306
00:25:50,245 --> 00:25:51,545
Masaya talaga ako.

307
00:25:52,717 --> 00:25:55,167
Nakagawa ka ng isa pang hakbang patungo sa iyong pangarap.

308
00:25:56,622 --> 00:25:58,841
Then I deserve a kiss on the cheek as a reward.

309
00:25:59,838 --> 00:26:01,285
Walang kinalaman iyon.

310
00:26:02,074 --> 00:26:02,768
konti na lang.

311
00:26:07,090 --> 00:26:09,078
Ilalabas mo ba ito para marinig ng iba?

312
00:26:10,223 --> 00:26:10,930
hindi ko alam.

313
00:26:13,176 --> 00:26:14,531
Kung gagawin ko talaga,

314
00:26:14,604 --> 00:26:16,570
Kailangan kong ayusin ito nang mas mahusay.

315
00:26:17,208 --> 00:26:19,271
At pagbutihin ang musika.

316
00:26:19,860 --> 00:26:20,967
Pagkatapos ay i-record ito sa isang studio.

317
00:26:21,579 --> 00:26:22,517
Mm.

318
00:26:24,302 --> 00:26:26,029
Gusto kong palabasin ito ni Arthit.

319
00:26:27,197 --> 00:26:28,915
Ayokong itago ito sa sarili ko.

320
00:26:29,722 --> 00:26:30,517
Mm.

321
00:26:32,068 --> 00:26:33,610
Tapos kapag natapos ko na,

322
00:26:35,321 --> 00:26:36,743
Hahayaan ko muna kayong makinig.

323
00:26:37,634 --> 00:26:38,195
Okay?

324
00:26:41,573 --> 00:26:42,343
maghihintay ako.

325
00:26:42,866 --> 00:26:43,380
Mm.

326
00:26:55,948 --> 00:26:58,238
Masyado kang gastador.

327
00:26:58,924 --> 00:27:00,682
Kung kikita ako ng pera, kailangan kong gastusin ito.

328
00:27:01,474 --> 00:27:02,597
Bakit i-save ito?

329
00:27:03,505 --> 00:27:05,554
At kung isang araw maubos ang iyong ipon,

330
00:27:06,118 --> 00:27:06,982
ano gagawin mo

331
00:27:07,241 --> 00:27:08,696
Ibig sabihin hindi pa ako mayaman.

332
00:27:09,312 --> 00:27:10,882
Tingnan mo ang best friend kong si Jo.

333
00:27:11,358 --> 00:27:12,417
Napakayaman niya kaya ang kanyang ipon

334
00:27:12,672 --> 00:27:14,360
ay ang pera na hindi niya nagastos.

335
00:27:16,574 --> 00:27:18,226
Hindi ka makapaniwala, Arthit.

336
00:27:19,549 --> 00:27:20,980
I really love it kapag sinasabi mo ang pangalan ko.

337
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:25,878
Arthit.

338
00:27:26,845 --> 00:27:27,568
Arthit.

339
00:27:28,706 --> 00:27:29,250
Hmm?

340
00:27:30,299 --> 00:27:31,145
Arthit.

341
00:27:34,231 --> 00:27:34,748
Oh.

342
00:27:35,296 --> 00:27:37,282
So, sinabi mo sa pamilya mo ang tungkol sa amin, di ba?

343
00:27:37,896 --> 00:27:38,786
ginawa ko.

344
00:27:41,005 --> 00:27:41,767
Ano ang sinabi nila?

345
00:27:43,007 --> 00:27:45,075
Medyo nabigla si Papa at Dad.

346
00:27:45,709 --> 00:27:48,884
Niyaya kami ni Lola para maghapunan.

347
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:50,574
So, pupunta tayo?

348
00:27:51,417 --> 00:27:53,057
Hindi ba magiging komportable si Arthit?

349
00:27:53,474 --> 00:27:54,004
Hmm?

350
00:27:54,665 --> 00:27:55,354
Ako?

351
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:56,349
Hindi komportable?

352
00:27:56,595 --> 00:27:57,097
Mm.

353
00:27:58,185 --> 00:28:00,835
Panoorin mo lang akong mapagtagumpayan ang pamilya mo.

354
00:28:01,383 --> 00:28:02,349
makikita mo.

355
00:28:05,231 --> 00:28:06,528
Pagkatapos ay dadalhin kita doon.

356
00:28:12,231 --> 00:28:12,924
Hey.

357
00:28:14,740 --> 00:28:17,315
Paano nagkakilala ang Papa at Papa mo?

358
00:28:19,389 --> 00:28:21,179
Si Papa ang love at first sight ni Dad.

359
00:28:21,571 --> 00:28:23,266
Nagkita sila sa isang café sa London.

360
00:28:29,758 --> 00:28:31,082
Pag-ibig sa unang tingin?

361
00:28:32,469 --> 00:28:32,967
Mm.

362
00:28:36,805 --> 00:28:38,035
Ngunit

363
00:28:38,589 --> 00:28:40,602
I guess hindi love at first sight ang sa amin.

364
00:28:41,881 --> 00:28:44,365
Medyo natagalan ako

365
00:28:45,085 --> 00:28:46,588
para magsimulang magkagusto sayo.

366
00:28:48,711 --> 00:28:52,585
Hindi ko maisip kung ano ang magiging hitsura nito

367
00:28:54,897 --> 00:28:56,105
kung hindi ka lumipat sa katabi.

368
00:28:57,542 --> 00:29:00,072
Magkakilala sana kami sa ibang paraan.

369
00:29:01,262 --> 00:29:01,720
Hmm?

370
00:29:03,314 --> 00:29:03,976
Bakit?

371
00:29:05,370 --> 00:29:06,442
Pumunta ako sa isang manghuhula.

372
00:29:08,391 --> 00:29:09,072
Seryoso?

373
00:29:09,992 --> 00:29:10,782
Mm.

374
00:29:12,093 --> 00:29:13,474
Soulmates tayo.

375
00:29:14,943 --> 00:29:16,103
Mm...

376
00:29:16,921 --> 00:29:18,287
So ibig sabihin

377
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,580
kahit anong mangyari,

378
00:29:22,562 --> 00:29:24,121
sana magkasama tayo, diba?

379
00:29:26,642 --> 00:29:27,217
Mm.

380
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,509
Galing din ba yan sa manghuhula?

381
00:29:32,394 --> 00:29:33,346
Hindi, galing iyon sa puso ko.

382
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:36,754
Damn.

383
00:29:43,099 --> 00:29:44,786
Itutok ang iyong mga mata sa kalsada.

384
00:29:45,389 --> 00:29:46,514
Mag-ingat sa pagmamaneho.

385
00:29:49,357 --> 00:29:50,700
Gusto ko lang makauwi ng mabilis.

386
00:29:59,571 --> 00:30:00,014
Tara na.

387
00:30:08,767 --> 00:30:10,231
Papa, Tatay.

388
00:30:10,398 --> 00:30:13,814
Halika dito. namiss kita.

389
00:30:14,477 --> 00:30:17,983
- Na-miss ka namin. Maligayang pagdating sa bahay.
- Namiss din kita.

390
00:30:18,365 --> 00:30:19,320
- Hello.
- Ikinagagalak kitang makilala.

391
00:30:29,487 --> 00:30:31,598
Medyo matagal na tayong hindi nagkita

392
00:30:31,924 --> 00:30:34,253
bakit tumaba ka, K'John?

393
00:30:34,727 --> 00:30:36,493
Iyon ang nagpapakain sa kanya.

394
00:30:36,712 --> 00:30:40,019
Parang pinapakain din niya ang anak ko?

395
00:30:41,826 --> 00:30:44,297
Ang chubby ng cheeks mo!

396
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:48,342
Sige, pasok na tayo sa loob. Naghihintay si lola.

397
00:30:48,970 --> 00:30:49,945
Tara na sa loob.

398
00:30:50,011 --> 00:30:50,680
Tara na.

399
00:31:01,851 --> 00:31:02,862
Paumanhin saglit.

400
00:31:02,970 --> 00:31:03,494
Oh?

401
00:31:04,441 --> 00:31:05,374
Nasaan ang apo ko?

402
00:31:07,423 --> 00:31:08,939
Khun Phuangthong.

403
00:31:09,115 --> 00:31:14,170
Kumusta ka apo? I’m so happy to see you.

404
00:31:14,308 --> 00:31:16,136
Sobrang na-miss kita, Khun Phuangthong.

405
00:31:16,241 --> 00:31:17,779
namiss din kita.

406
00:31:21,515 --> 00:31:22,025
Oh.

407
00:31:22,121 --> 00:31:22,565
Ah.

408
00:31:23,145 --> 00:31:23,957
Halika maupo ka.

409
00:31:26,134 --> 00:31:26,712
Oo, ginang.

410
00:31:32,642 --> 00:31:33,918
Sobrang gwapo.

411
00:31:34,364 --> 00:31:36,204
Parehong anak at apo.

412
00:31:36,506 --> 00:31:40,534
Alam mo talaga kung paano maghanap ng manugang at apo na gusto ko.

413
00:31:41,413 --> 00:31:43,629
Tutulungan ko muna si Papa sa kusina.

414
00:31:44,493 --> 00:31:45,238
Sige, sige.

415
00:31:45,466 --> 00:31:46,654
Sige na mag-usap.

416
00:31:46,712 --> 00:31:47,328
Okay.

417
00:31:51,776 --> 00:31:53,065
Ano ang iyong pangalan

418
00:31:53,299 --> 00:31:54,429
Ang pangalan ko ay Arthit.

419
00:31:54,908 --> 00:31:57,197
Hmm, magandang pangalan iyon.

420
00:31:58,435 --> 00:31:59,982
At ano ang iyong pangalan?

421
00:32:00,201 --> 00:32:02,114
Phuangthong.

422
00:32:02,253 --> 00:32:04,635
Hmm, magandang pangalan iyon.

423
00:32:06,047 --> 00:32:07,037
Ang binatang ito...

424
00:32:07,539 --> 00:32:08,346
Hindi masama sa lahat.

425
00:32:13,022 --> 00:32:14,751
Eto, tulungan mo ako.

426
00:32:15,136 --> 00:32:16,248
ayos lang.

427
00:32:18,189 --> 00:32:19,906
May gusto daw sa kanya si Lola.

428
00:32:20,149 --> 00:32:21,748
Mukhang magkakasundo sila.

429
00:32:22,688 --> 00:32:23,520
Parang ganun.

430
00:32:25,617 --> 00:32:27,813
Hindi ba papasok sina Papa at Papa ngayon?

431
00:32:28,114 --> 00:32:29,183
Hindi.

432
00:32:29,514 --> 00:32:30,844
Alam naming darating ka.

433
00:32:31,482 --> 00:32:33,035
Nag leave muna ako.

434
00:32:33,549 --> 00:32:34,531
Oh.

435
00:32:37,952 --> 00:32:38,595
Papa.

436
00:32:41,502 --> 00:32:42,514
Okay ka lang ba dito?

437
00:32:45,934 --> 00:32:47,097
ako.

438
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:51,680
Iginagalang ko ang iyong desisyon.

439
00:32:52,351 --> 00:32:53,207
Ngunit…

440
00:32:54,208 --> 00:32:55,974
Hindi ko pa siya lubos na kilala.

441
00:32:56,394 --> 00:32:58,850
Kaya hayaan ko muna siyang bantayan.

442
00:32:59,391 --> 00:33:00,180
Oo naman.

443
00:33:01,543 --> 00:33:02,475
Ang apo ko...

444
00:33:02,891 --> 00:33:04,641
Siya ay isang tahimik na bata mula noong siya ay maliit.

445
00:33:05,150 --> 00:33:09,826
Noong kindergarten, isinulat ng guro na hindi siya masayahin.

446
00:33:09,859 --> 00:33:11,920
Hindi masyadong palakaibigan.

447
00:33:12,542 --> 00:33:13,248
Mm.

448
00:33:13,352 --> 00:33:17,120
Tinawag pa nila ang kanyang tagapag-alaga, nag-aalala na baka may problema sa pamilya.

449
00:33:18,420 --> 00:33:20,022
Kahit ngayon, hindi siya masyadong nagsasalita.

450
00:33:21,271 --> 00:33:23,400
Noon, sa tuwing may tinatanong ako sa kanya...

451
00:33:23,705 --> 00:33:24,485
Sasagot lang siya—

452
00:33:24,845 --> 00:33:25,528
Mm.

453
00:33:25,829 --> 00:33:26,613
Mm-hmm.

454
00:33:28,557 --> 00:33:31,471
Sa totoo lang, halos wala kaming maayos na pag-uusap, Lola.

455
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:34,700
Ginang.

456
00:33:35,696 --> 00:33:39,321
Hindi kailangang maging pormal.
Magsalita ka lang sa paraang karaniwan mong ginagawa.

457
00:33:39,690 --> 00:33:41,771
- Tulad ng kung paano ako madalas makipag-usap ...
- Mm.

458
00:33:42,619 --> 00:33:44,134
Kaya mo ba yan?

459
00:33:44,229 --> 00:33:46,400
kaya ko.

460
00:33:46,857 --> 00:33:50,145
Huwag lang magsalita ng English tulad ni Gavin.

461
00:33:50,223 --> 00:33:51,801
Hindi ko maintindihan ang isang salita.

462
00:33:54,081 --> 00:33:55,635
Noong una, noong si Phai

463
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:59,404
pinakilala sa akin, sobrang na-stress ako.

464
00:33:59,425 --> 00:34:01,026
- Mm.
- Hindi naman sa hindi ko siya gusto.

465
00:34:01,170 --> 00:34:05,346
Pero paulit-ulit niyang sinasabi ang mga bagay na hindi ko maintindihan.
Paano kung binabastos niya ako?

466
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:07,056
- Oh.
- Kahit ngayon,

467
00:34:07,717 --> 00:34:11,447
Mahirap pa rin siyang kausapin.

468
00:34:11,740 --> 00:34:15,220
Ang masasabi ko lang ay “Hey, hey, come on.”

469
00:34:19,234 --> 00:34:21,614
So paano mo nagustuhan ang apo ko?

470
00:34:23,425 --> 00:34:24,533
hindi ako sigurado.

471
00:34:25,493 --> 00:34:27,088
Pagkatapos ng ilang oras na magkasama,

472
00:34:27,293 --> 00:34:28,891
Nagsimula lang akong magkagusto kay Dao sa pagiging Dao.

473
00:34:30,936 --> 00:34:31,829
Hindi ko talaga maipaliwanag.

474
00:34:32,613 --> 00:34:33,311
nakikita ko.

475
00:34:33,884 --> 00:34:35,868
Paano naman sa university? May mga kaibigan ba siya?

476
00:34:36,125 --> 00:34:36,637
ginagawa niya.

477
00:34:37,792 --> 00:34:39,226
Mukhang medyo close sila.

478
00:34:39,669 --> 00:34:41,247
Mabait silang lahat.

479
00:34:41,779 --> 00:34:42,528
Bagama't…

480
00:34:43,475 --> 00:34:45,370
Ang ilan sa kanila ay maaaring medyo bastos.

481
00:34:47,327 --> 00:34:50,432
Bakit? Nag-aalala ka ba na walang mga kaibigan si Dao?

482
00:34:51,478 --> 00:34:52,958
Syempre ako.

483
00:34:53,207 --> 00:34:54,402
Hindi ko alam kung bakit, pero…

484
00:34:54,798 --> 00:34:55,952
Daotok—

485
00:34:56,278 --> 00:34:58,755
Parati siyang umaakit ng masasamang tao.

486
00:34:59,192 --> 00:35:00,518
Oh.

487
00:35:00,776 --> 00:35:02,125
Ngunit pagkarinig nito,

488
00:35:02,859 --> 00:35:04,091
gumaan ang pakiramdam ko.

489
00:35:04,628 --> 00:35:07,813
Sa pag-aalaga mo sa kanya,
Hindi na ako nag-aalala.

490
00:35:11,357 --> 00:35:15,490
Hindi ko sasabihin na ako ay isang mabuting tao,
pero pagdating sa pag-aalaga sa Daotok—

491
00:35:16,025 --> 00:35:19,583
Ipinapangako ko na gagawin ko ang aking makakaya.

492
00:35:21,601 --> 00:35:22,557
pangako ko.

493
00:35:29,693 --> 00:35:30,920
Medyo maliit ang kwarto.

494
00:35:31,154 --> 00:35:32,265
Pwede bang dito ka matulog?

495
00:35:33,522 --> 00:35:34,364
Maliit?

496
00:35:35,182 --> 00:35:36,594
Natulog ako sa mas masikip na espasyo kaysa dito.

497
00:35:44,682 --> 00:35:45,189
Hey.

